## JWT: deps.py → get_uid() — barcha endpointlar shu dependency dan
## CORS: allow_origin_regex — wildcard "*" TAQIQLANGAN
## Rate limit: Redis (deps.py) + in-memory GC (middleware)
## Export: user_id tekshiruvi — boshqa user faylini yuklab olish MUMKIN EMAS

## Pydantic v2:
# .model_dump() ishlatiladi (eski .dict() TAQIQLANGAN)

