## PUL_NORM backreference:
# r"\g<1>000"  ✅ (named backreference)
# r"\1000"     ❌ (Python \100 = '@' octal deb o'qiydi!)

## Sheva pattern:
# r"\b" + word + r"\b"  → so'z chegarasi
# re.IGNORECASE | re.UNICODE  → doim

